{"title":"花儿三首","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":12,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"花儿三首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔甘肃临夏回族自治州〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贫下中农骨头硬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高山的红松冬夏青，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好红松，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雪里它长得更青。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贫下中农骨头硬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骨头硬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂风暴雨推不动。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贫下中农要革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牢牢地记在心中。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远跟着毛泽东，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向前进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社花越开是越红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学习何家庄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁不夸何家庄民兵连，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给我们树立了标杆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贫下中农往前站，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掌政权，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"攥紧了手中的枪杆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“四严”的名声传得红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们临夏人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要学个革命的精神。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦练硬练加油练，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好好地练，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请我们的毛主席来看看。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望玉门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在祁连山上望玉门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石油城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它是我们祖国的宝盆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石油城的英雄骨头硬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"靠自家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摔掉了洋人的拐棍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"玉门人名声满天下红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的手指着玉门。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}